						<p>On a slab lying in front of the ruined Śiva temple in the village.</p>						

						<p>Fragmentary. Seems to record the gift of land as <hi rend="italic">daśavanda</hi> and refers to a copper-plate grant of which this is evidently a copy. In characters of the 11th century A.D.</p>						

